title: Mid Night Club Pt.2 - Inside Story of Team Mid Night
description:
In the final installment of the series, James and Nolan explore more of the lore of the infamous underground Japanese race team, The Mid Night Club. Plus, James and Nolan pass on a message from an actual member of Mid Night.
Follow James on IG and Twitter @jamespumphrey  
Follow Nolan on IG and Twitter @nolanjsykes 
Follow Donut @donutmedia, and subscribe to our Youtube and Facebook channels!
